Question: Each image contains an old-fashioned TV with controls on the right of its screen, and no TV has a lit screen or picture displayed on the screen.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Xo6lsZgzgfQ/maxresdefault.jpg

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/dd/5a/2e/dd5a2e719317cc5bea533766446b13a1.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there an old-fashioned TV in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there an old-fashioned TV in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the controls on the right of the screen?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the controls on the right of the screen?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the TV screen lit?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the TV screen lit?')
ANSWER6=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a picture displayed on the screen?')
ANSWER7=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a picture displayed on the screen?')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and not {ANSWER4} and not {ANSWER6}')
ANSWER9=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and not {ANSWER5} and not {ANSWER7}')
ANSWER10=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER8} and {ANSWER9}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER10)
```
